anier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Oui je le veux. Je [maybe:film] le reste. Non, mais, esti… Si t'es pas capable, dis les pas.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Denis Vanier","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15#t=155,165"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Laughter.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Audience","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15#t=165,168"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"J'ai pas besoin du livre.","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"\"Marie\"","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","motivation":"tagging"}],"target":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15#t=168,170"},{"@context":"http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld","type":"Annotation","motivation":["commenting","tagging"],"id":"https://spokenweb.github.io/Ultimatumi1985/denis_vanier_at_ultimatum_festival_1985_05_04/canvas/15/page1","body":[{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Speaks [unintelligable].","format":"text/plain","motivation":"commenting"},{"type":"TextualBody","value":"Denis Vanier","format":"text/plain","purpose":"tagging","mot